\begin_layout Itemize

\emph on
Sentiment analysis
\emph default
.
 Collect tweets with a given hashtag (for example #windows8).
 Train a classifier that predicts peoples' sentiments regarding the object
 of the hashtag.
 Note that these types of projects requires you to label the sentiment 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

by hand
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 for each of the tweets, which takes some time, but typically goes faster
 than you would think, once you get going.
\end_layout

